1. The objective was to evaluate the effectiveness of lanreotide Autogel® 120 mg.
2. Lanreotide Autogel® 120 mg was administered every 4–8 weeks.
3. The comparison was made with lanreotide microparticles 30 mg.
4. Lanreotide microparticles 30 mg was administered every 1–2 weeks.
5. The context of the evaluation is in controlling acromegaly.

messages.content:
Statement: Our objective was to evaluate whether lanreotide Autogel® 120 mg, every 4–8 weeks, was as effective in controlling acromegaly as lanreotide microparticles 30 mg, every 1–2 weeks.
